==================== Input ====================
# Explicit-key comment placement: by column between the key and the `:`,
# and as the value's middle comment after the `:`.
? # between ? and key
  - seq key
: # after the colon (value middle comment)
  - value
    # deeper than the PREVIOUS item = its collection value's end comment
plain: separator
? deep
    # deeper than the item, before `:` = key end comment
: 1
? same
# at the item column = leads the `: ` line
: 2
? bare-no-value # same-line comment keeps the explicit form
? normalized
: implicit stays

